":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"之鋒一出聲，馬上踢爆分化五毛所謂休息唔裝修既風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634714</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"28c6c5403e5b2a6bf010f1e2c1ba7ade53c307eb","tid":1635233,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"出黎"},{"pid":"3a3ce085b3f00eb70a28a3bcff52673ff92c096c","tid":1635233,"uid":160842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"6ee3907ec4d81b605304ce3d23a5899c263e56a9","tid":1635233,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:38:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fcec705f3a03ed552801aa827e6d57ccc3f50d7","tid":1635233,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac657a70aa6a50a17dda60366948c4087759016d","tid":1635233,"uid":86119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35a45b2e41553c5f453db090fa07016f29673daa","tid":1635233,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd317dd0f3b1f0561d384e464804a2cbd9872ca","tid":1635233,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2